author: Marvel Entertainment
description:
It's game night in the Marvel universe and everyone is out of character. Can this unlikely team of villains playing heroes work together to overcome the greatest role playing experience in all existence? Galactus has his doubts... Grab your lucky dice and don't forget the snacks because tonight we roll for victory in the Marvel Multiverse Role Playing Game.
